  <!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm"/>

   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.property_assignment_select">
The property_assignment_select is an extensible list of alternate data types. It provides a mechanism to 
refer to one of the listed types. 
<p>This Select type shall not be extended, adding activity data types.</p>
      </ext_description>
  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm  Entity: Assigned_property 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property">
An <b>Assigned_property</b> specifies a property that is assigned to product data.
      </ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm  Entity: Assigned_property  Attribute: name 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property.name">
the string that specifies the kind of property.
        </ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm  Entity: Assigned_property  Attribute: description 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property.description">
a text that provides further information about the property. The value of this attribute need not be specified.
        </ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm  Entity: Assigned_property  Attribute: described_element 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property.described_element">
the element to which the property is assigned.
        </ext_description>
				
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property.id">
a text that provides further an identifier for the Assigned_property. The value of this attribute need not be specified.
        </ext_description>
  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm  Entity: Applied_independent_property  
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Applied_independent_property">
An <b>Applied_independent_Assigned_property</b> is an association of an <b>Assigned_property</b> with an <b>Independent_property</b>. 
It characterizes the fact that the Assigned_property is the application of the Independent_property to product data.
        </ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm  Entity: Applied_independent_Assigned_property Attribute: base_Assigned_property  
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Applied_independent_property.base_independent_property">
the Independent_property from which the type of the Assigned_property is derived.</ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_assignment_arm  Entity: Applied_independent_property Attribute: name
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Applied_independent_property.SELF\Assigned_property.name">
the name of the Assigned_property, derived from the property_type of the Independent_property.</ext_description>

 <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_representation_arm  Entity: property_representation 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
  <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Property_representation">
A Property_representation specifies an association between an Assigned_property and one of its representations. 
      </ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_representation_arm  Entity: property_representation  Attribute: item 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Property_representation.property">
the property being represented.
        </ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_representation_arm  Entity: property_representation  Attribute: rep 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Property_representation.rep">
the Representation associated with the property.
        </ext_description>

  <!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Property_representation_arm  Entity: property_representation  Attribute: role 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Property_representation.role">
the string that sepecifies the role of the representation with respect to the property.
<example>'simplified representation' is an example of role.</example>
   </ext_description>
				
   <ext_description linkend="Property_assignment_arm.Property_representation.description">
a text that provides further information about the Property_representation. The value of this attribute need not be specified.
    </ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>
